        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-purple-500">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">The Design-Build Advantage</h2>
            
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
              Our turnkey design-build approach streamlines your project from initial concept through final completion. 
              With integrated design and construction teams, we deliver faster, more cost-effective solutions while 
              maintaining single-source accountability for your entire project.
