                <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-3xl">🎯</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Single Point Accountability</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">One contract, one team responsible for everything</p>
              </div>

              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-3xl">⚡</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Faster Delivery</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Design and construction overlap saves 20-30% time</p>
              </div>

              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-3xl">💰</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Cost Certainty</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Fixed price from day one, no change order surprises</p>
              </div>

              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-3xl">🏆</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Quality Assurance</h3>
