              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>• Complete buildout</li>
                <li>• All trades included</li>
                <li>• Quality control</li>
                <li>• Safety management</li>
                <li>• Schedule control</li>
                <li>• Site supervision</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

